Package edu.uiowa.cs.warp

Class Options

java.lang.Object
edu.uiowa.cs.warp.Options
public class Options extends Object
Options used to build the Warp System. Default Options are defined here, but they can be overridden by command-line options or the graphical user interface.
Version:
2.0 Fall 2025
Author:
sgoddard

    • scaleFont

      private void scaleFont(String component, double scaleFactor)
      Scale the font size of the component by the scale factor. If the scale factor == 1, then no change. If less than 1, then shrinks. If greater than 1, then increases.
      Parameters:
      component - whose font will be scaled
      scaleFactor - amount by which the font is scaled
